data.description: Price Improvement! Discover the perfect blend of country charm and modern living in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a generous .89-acre lot located in Cross City is ready for your personal touch. The light and bright open floorplan offers an eat-in kitchen with granite countertops with additional seating at the breakfast bar, rich wood-toned cabinetry and the built-in pantry cabinet offers pull-out drawers and collapsible shelves. The great room boasts a fireplace with direct access to separate dining area.  A secondary family room offers additional space for relaxation and entertainment with stone surround fireplace and bay window adding character and plenty of natural light. The split floor plan offers privacy with an oversized primary ensuite with walk-in closet. Primary bathroom features dual vanity, water closet, soaker tub and linen closet. Secondary bedrooms offer wall closets and full bathroom has remodeled shower. Enjoy the four-season lanai and screens and windows year-round. Attached two car garage houses the washer/dryer. Circular driveway, additional 20x20 garage with service door offers wash tub and 220 power and additional shed is ready for customization. Some of the windows have been replaced and new hot water heater in 2021. 26 gauge Tuff Ribbed Metal Roof System. This property is your canvas to create the perfect home that suits your lifestyle. Whether you are looking for a peaceful retreat, a place to put down roots, or a renovation project, this home offers the ideal foundation.
